descriptionHTML:
This watch face includes design and technology.

This watch face is compatible with every smartwatch with android wear and ideal for round smartwatches.

*it doesn't support other operative systems like Samsung galaxy gear.

To install the watch face you must have the official Android Wear application and your watch must be paired with your device.

Custom features:

🔹HD quality watch face
🔋Battery indicator
⌚ Date
